\psi(x) = \log x - \frac{1}{2x} + \sum_{k=1}^{\infty}\frac{\zeta(1-2k)}{x^{2k}}
\int_0^1 \sin(\pi x)\psi(x+n) dx = \frac{2}{\pi} \log n + O(\frac{1}{n})\tag{*3}
