\lim_{n\to\infty} \left(\int_0^{\frac{\pi}{2}} \left|\frac{\sin((2n+1)x)}{\sin x}\right| dx - \frac{2}{\pi} \log n\right) = \frac{2}{\pi} \log\frac{4}{\pi} - \int_0^1 \sin(\pi x)\psi(x) dx \tag{*4}
